title: Mega Mission series - H.I. Larry [Epub & Mobi] { KT }
description:
Mega Mission series
Author: H.I. Larry 



Book 1: Base Camp
This time it's going to take more than 24 hours...

Base Camp

Zac Power and his spy agency GIB are facing their biggest challenge yet - but so much of the mission is a mystery!

Can Zac stop the enemy, even when he doesn't know who it is?



Book 2: Code Red
This time its going to take more than 24 hours.....

Code Red

Zac Power's evil double is on the loose, and only the real Zac can stop him.

So why won't GIB tell Zac what's REALLY going on?



Book 3: Moon Rider
Zac is shooting into space on his first lunar mission!

But he has no idea what's in store for him on the dark side of the moon...



Book 4: High Stakes
Zac has to beat the ZacBot to GIB HQ - or his agency will be totally wiped out.

GIB have no idea what's coming, and only Zac can save the day...


Genre: Childrens | Adventure | Fantasy
